{"tid":1441802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警玩無差別攻擊，搞斯德哥爾摩心理戰可以點做？","createTime":"2019-08-10T17:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T07:00:48.000Z","uid":290390,"like":121,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"6326008cd118cfbbae4de365860d0dd1516841a1","tid":1441802,"uid":290390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:58:12.000Z","msg":"斯德哥爾摩症候群大概就係當你被壓倒性的力量所脅逼，你會同情及認同壓逼者。<br />\n<br />\n黑警近期無差別攻擊市民，可能都係想勾起呢種心理，令民眾憎恨示威者，至少不再支持他們的行動。要拆唔係無辦法，好簡單直接，但難度高。<br />\n<br />\n你試下幻想班遊擊示威者係俠盜羅賓漢一伙，佢地正面打唔贏邪惡城主的軍隊，於是不斷遊擊混入民眾當中，城主奈佢唔何。僵持不下，跟住城主初時就無差別殺傷平民，的確，市民敢怒不敢言，但係同時都不敢隨便窩藏羅賓漢黨人。<br />\n<br />\n雖然羅賓漢少左掩護，但係要殲滅佢地仍然好難，於是城主就懸賞，邊個幫手供出甚至活捉羅賓漢黨羽，重重有賞。於是全城齊篤灰，呢個就真係民意逆轉喇<br />\n<br />\n咁羅賓漢要點樣扳回件事呢？<br />\n<br />\n就係要示範俾民眾睇，城主軍隊雖然好強，但係我地有機會打得贏。換言之伏擊又好，set traps又好，在某d情況下重創城主軍隊，甚至可能只係搶糧車或囚車，咁樣民間就仍然會視羅賓漢為反抗希望象徵。<br />\n<br />\n回到香港，現在齋撚狗，還擊係偏少，時間一長，就變成民間瘟神，因為群眾好快會被訓練到一見示威者就知道自己要被捲入受到懲罰，示威者走得甩而自己仲要硬食，咁就會怨恨班人係搞事。<br />\n<br />\n換轉，如果新聞報左幾單黑警被不知名人士襲擊，五花大綁無著衫，春袋有大大個唇印，咁大家會知呢班人係黎懲惡打奸，而且黑警並非畫面上咁無敵，咁就會同仇敵愾，持續站在示威者一方<br />\n<br />\n瓦解斯德哥爾摩心理戰的方法，就係要令受害者（民眾）明白壞人的力量不是絕對，是有機會可以擊破的。咁佢地依附強者求存的心態就不會被啟動。講明唔係鼓勵任何犯法行為，照做就後果自負呀下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33cd454fb26e11ca8f74e51ed2bc7066799fee5b","tid":1441802,"uid":290390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:00:17.000Z","msg":"先自推十連發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8706edd71746307827dc9ee68d4593e2723a153a","tid":1441802,"uid":290390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:01:42.000Z","msg":"自推第九hit <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad1516bd680cfb784f5a27223bd456a96d3662f","tid":1441802,"uid":116734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bcbcff43c6dae7b56ad70f0b16f98c65d99e59","tid":1441802,"uid":290390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"自推八，發發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f092cb62fe0e1a61f5674de9469a4287378264b","tid":1441802,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc988232f26f5747762d570df308550f5b608bcb","tid":1441802,"uid":290390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:03:57.000Z","msg":"自推七，一碌柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b99ae080830d616301e81daef5ea139ac61a01","tid":1441802,"uid":290390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:05:08.000Z","msg":"自推六一鑊熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6507af0de5d1f1ba722f062191c692b69fe00e","tid":1441802,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:05:47.000Z","msg":"麻包袋"},{"pid":"b19de5e9eccca17196665d2173bcd915d553f1df","tid":1441802,"uid":290390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:06:21.000Z","msg":"自推五。<br />\n麻包袋講左九世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc9d99641e3238bb809602d03978d7e203a8095","tid":1441802,"uid":287594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T1