10T18:19:36.000Z","msg":"千萬千萬千萬千萬不要犯法"},{"pid":"c62ee2e419ef973eabb793069d22cec16d043d17","tid":1441802,"uid":290390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:26:54.000Z","msg":"好，方法就寫左，太眼訓唔諗了"},{"pid":"bdfa8021803f8bd944afc064f8617d9da0065b3b","tid":1441802,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKJm9B6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKJm9B6.jpg&h=62cfb11f&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>出沒注意</strong>⚠️<strong>時刻保持警覺 獨立思考！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>凡事抱有懷疑態度！不輕信他人！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9a63e18de7022ab49d694fd6884deab80cb6c86b","tid":1441802,"uid":290390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"屌，駛唔駛一見P牌仔就嘈呀"},{"pid":"3b81d0ae89031ee9e0db48fcd520b7a029b7ce52","tid":1441802,"uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bdfa8021803f8bd944afc064f8617d9da0065b3b","tid":1441802,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKJm9B6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKJm9B6.jpg&h=62cfb11f&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>出沒注意</strong>⚠️<strong>時刻保持警覺 獨立思考！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>凡事抱有懷疑態度！不輕信他人！</strong></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:50:02.000Z","msg":"呢篇好文黎喎<br />\np乜柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同意好多p牌都係3毛黎<br />\n但呢篇的確有料喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff823403590c9494e280b40287e98ca52e669a7f","tid":1441802,"uid":290390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b81d0ae89031ee9e0db48fcd520b7a029b7ce52","tid":1441802,"uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bdfa8021803f8bd944afc064f8617d9da0065b3b","tid":1441802,"uid":251001,"like